<br>
If you grouped with my alts would you be able to tell I do not know how to play the class? Probably not at all.<br>
<br>
I have a 65 wizard...we wizards love to research things so I research any alt I am going to play for weeks before I even create them. Learning all the tricks to the class and where and how they fit into a group or raid. <br>
<br>
Would I trade that 49 days I spent getting my wizard to lvl 50 for todays high speed journey to lvl 50? Not on your life!!! Those 49 days were amazing, filled with wonder, awe, excitement, fear, and sometimes incredible frustration and endless downtime. <br>
<br>
